Artist and filmmaker Richard Swarbrick will be animating the best plays from the conference finals and NBA Finals, with music by Empathy Test. Swarbrick collaborated with ESPN last year to celebrate the best moments in NBA Finals history in his signature style. Enjoy the latest animations here: Manu Ginobili's big fourth-quarter 3 in Game 6 of the West finals Paul George's dagger over LeBron in Game 5 of the East finals LeBron's reverse dunk in Game 4 of the East finals Serge Ibaka's block party in Game 3 of the West finals